== Corporate structure ==

EDSA, Inc. is a [[privately held company]]. {{Asof|2012}}, the firm Is headed by Douglas C. Smith, who is the president of the company<ref>{{cite web |title=EDSA Leadership Page |url=https://www.edsaplan.com/leadership/ |website=EDSA}}</ref> and a principal of one of the 13 design studios.

